<A>__{norman comes out of mary's cabin, closes the door carefully behind him, goes along the porch to his office, goes in. we stay outside. immediately, the "vacancy" sign goes off, and then the motel sign goes off. as camera goes closer to the office, the lights within go off and we hear a closet door opening and then the sound of a pail being picked up. norman comes out of office, closes door, looks cautiously about, goes along porch, carrying pail with mop in it, goes into mary's cabin, closing the door after him.}
